---
import Layout from "../layouts/layouts.astro";
import MapEmbed from "../components/MapEmbed.astro";
---

<Layout title="Nearby Restaurants" currentPath={Astro.url.pathname}


<section class="heroCard">
	<div class="introGrid">
		<div>
            <h1>Best Restaurants &amp; Bars</h1>
			<p>
				One of the best parts of staying at Nardelli is eating your way around Umbria and Tuscany — the “green heart of Italy” on one side,
				and some of the world’s most famous food and wine landscapes on the other. Keep an eye out for local favourites like <strong>torta al testo</strong>
				(a warm, rustic flatbread), Umbria’s excellent olive oil, and the simple, seasonal dishes that make even a quick lunch feel special.
				Across the Tuscan border, you’ll find <strong>pecorino</strong> (especially around Pienza), big, bold reds like <strong>Brunello di Montalcino</strong>,
				and the region’s iconic <strong>Chianina</strong> beef. Whether you’re after an easy family pizza, a relaxed lakeside aperitivo, or a memorable dinner,
				the places below are our go-to picks — and the map further down has extra notes.
			</p>

            <p style="color: var(--muted); font-weight: 600; margin-top: 10px;">
	        <strong>Family tip:</strong> dinner service in most restaurants around the area typically starts from around <strong>19:00</strong>, which is worth knowing if you’re planning around younger children.
            </p>

			<h2 style="margin-top: 14px;">Best Restaurants &amp; Bars</h2>
			<ul class="bestList">
            <li>
                Best restaurants in Castiglione del Lago: <strong><a href="https://maps.app.goo.gl/zMW2GPK3mEPDhKAB9" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Osteria Nova</a></strong> &amp; <strong><a href="https://maps.app.goo.gl/qBXeSowm9UEMVaL7A" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Ristorante La Terrazza</a></strong>
            </li>
            <li>
                Best pizza in Castiglione del Lago: <strong><a href="https://maps.app.goo.gl/d4Gp6sy9Y1TftEox7" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Ristorante La Cantina</a></strong>
            </li>
            <li>
                Best pizza on the lake: <strong><a href="https://maps.app.goo.gl/zcJmuCnH9tMAPqAm7" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Giramondo Ristorante Pizzeria</a></strong>
            </li>
            <li>
                Best beach bar: <strong><a href="https://maps.app.goo.gl/DpFRrNCo9xxx5rFK8" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Cafe Pescatore Praia</a></strong>
            </li>
            <li>
                Best village setting: <strong><a href="https://maps.app.goo.gl/btDQF23ZRfemdDbF7" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Panicale</a></strong>
            </li>
            <li>
                Best sushi: <strong><a href="https://maps.app.goo.gl/SVa9ZSDdKi2U8Br27" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Restaurant Sushi Mizu</a></strong>
            </li>
        </ul>
		</div>

		<img
			src="/photos/Restaurant.jpg"
			alt="Food and wine in Umbria and Tuscany"
			loading="lazy"
		/>
	</div>
</section>



<h2>Map</h2>
<p style="color: var(--muted); margin-top: -6px;">
	Click pinned items on the map for additional insight and detail.
</p>

<MapEmbed
	title="Local Restaurants, Bars & Cafes"
	src="https://www.google.com/maps/d/embed?mid=1s7yXs9jQ8JVRJrBzack_63GSfhvhT-E&ehbc=2E312F"
/>

<style>
	.heroCard {
		background: var(--card);
		border: 1px solid var(--border);
		border-radius: var(--radius);
		padding: 16px;
		margin: 12px 0 18px;
	}

	.introGrid {
		display: grid;
		gap: 16px;
		align-items: start;
	}

	.introGrid img {
		width: 100%;
		height: 260px;
		object-fit: cover;
		display: block;
		border-radius: calc(var(--radius) - 2px);
		border: 1px solid var(--border);
	}

	@media (min-width: 860px) {
		.introGrid {
			grid-template-columns: 1.1fr 0.9fr;
			align-items: center;
		}
		.introGrid img {
			height: 640px;
		}
	}

	.bestList {
		margin: 8px 0 0;
		padding-left: 20px;
	}

	.bestList li {
		margin: 8px 0;
	}
</style>
</Layout>